{"tid":160500,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我老豆竟然係我面前喊","createTime":"2017-03-17T17:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T06:51:34.000Z","uid":76399,"like":390,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"063548dcbac94198bebb20868adc1ac546e98979","tid":160500,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:52:53.000Z","msg":"話說早排冇野做，重睇鋼鍊FA<br />\n我就屎忽癢叫埋老豆一齊睇，點知佢真係陪我睇<br />\n每個星期日就同佢睇2~3集<br />\n今日終於睇到第63集，睇到賀恩漢死果陣，小弟都有啲眼濕濕，出盡奶力忍住啲眼淚。<br />\n誰不知我竟然聽到有啲怪聲，擰轉頭發現老豆眼有淚光，仲流埋馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就唔小心gap一聲笑左出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就扮去廁所，等老豆平伏吓，執執個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我出返廳嘅時候發現老豆個樣已經回復正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲問多佢一句，仲睇唔睇埋最後一集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢竟然話: 唔啦，有啲攰。下次先睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我笑左出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1086192279ed28a2cf14857dfe00d0f0d46144","tid":160500,"uid":72793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:54:26.000Z","msg":"好正，可以同老豆睇鋼鍊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36007c75640d2f8ef7ccb8827c125e586f807acc","tid":160500,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:55:48.000Z","msg":"有個咁嘅老豆幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7932c9c2dc9ed2ed8ec065123571dc6120576b","tid":160500,"uid":87860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87c4af1b63e545e8dcfc2c4a8d9405f60c0d94dd","tid":160500,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />